        <itemProvenance>Obtained in 2024 from a friend of Konijn’s mother; the friend found the DS along with some games in her water-damaged basement. The console originally belonged to the friend’s now-adult daughter, who had no interest in keeping it, so it was passed on to Konijn, who was very surprised to start up the console and find that it not only appeared to function normally, but still had battery life even after sitting in a basement for an estimated 15 years.</itemProvenance>
